snippet.textDisplay: In Hong Kong during flu peak season in public hospital you might have to wait up to 4-5 hours just to see one doctor. Because the government sector of Hong Kong for doctors is really low. Which means we have shortage of health workers but we still have the best healthcare service but we just have to wait longer which is of course annoying
